  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/13077393/ski-bundle-image-website.jpg" alt="Ski Bundle Offers" data-udi="umb://media/6d8549dacfe54a2583684882295ffb58" /><br />
<p style="text-align: left;">Banff is the heart and soul of SkiBig3, a ski area which should be on everyone’s bucket list. The Rocky Mountains, fresh powder, uncrowded slopes, spectacular scenery and not forgetting their famous hospitality make it a dream location for any skier. Lake Louise is a hamlett in Banff National Park and it’s the wilderness around the Lake that our guests talk about most. It’s perfect for a peaceful getaway with the luxury of the SkiBig3 on your doorstep.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">The only thing missing from Banff &amp; Lake Louise is you, and we’re here to bring the dream closer with our fantastic Early Booking Offers.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Book your 20/21 Winter break before 31<sup>st</sup> August to receive our best Early Booking Offers.</strong></p>
