<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Top offers for Banff &amp; Lake Louise</strong></h1>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a><a data-udi="umb://document/b000a1b6d2b8439a923cb559c15d4385" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b000a1b6d2b8439a923cb559c15d4385}" title="Moose Hotel &amp; Suites">Moose Hotels &amp; Suites</a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/b000a1b6d2b8439a923cb559c15d4385" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b000a1b6d2b8439a923cb559c15d4385}" title="Moose Hotel &amp; Suites">Banff</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13077378/les-brevieres-exterior-2.jpg" alt="Caribou Lodge in Banff" data-udi="umb://media/e62aeb38256141be8ebad68eeb8da8a9" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span>The newest hotel in Banff, this Deluxe 4 star plus is centrally situated a minute walk from the downtown Banff. Designed to mountain elegance with warm, rich and natural materials.</span><br /><br /><strong>25% off - book by 31st August</strong> <br /><br /><em>Not available on bookings between 23rd December - 2nd January.</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/b000a1b6d2b8439a923cb559c15d4385" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b000a1b6d2b8439a923cb559c15d4385}" title="Moose Hotel &amp; Suites"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b13219f7cfff4c59aa47caa452f4cae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b13219f7cfff4c59aa47caa452f4cae7}" title="Fairmont Banff Springs">Fairmont Banff Springs<br />Banff</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13077375/du-golf-les-arcs.jpg" alt="Fairmont Banff Springs in Banff" data-udi="umb://media/b64a281019ad471f934a2e1832c9c61b" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">A world famous hotel, the old Baronial splendor of the Fairmont Banff Springs never fails to amaze. Virtually a resort in itself with superb views of the wilderness.<br /><br /><strong>30% off - book by 31st August</strong> <br /><br /><em>Not available on bookings between 23rd December - 2nd January and 12th February - 14th February.</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b13219f7cfff4c59aa47caa452f4cae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b13219f7cfff4c59aa47caa452f4cae7}" title="Fairmont Banff Springs"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a><a data-udi="umb://document/a04e6e8524a4497fb22cc5de99faf4da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a04e6e8524a4497fb22cc5de99faf4da}" title="Fairmont Chateau Lake Louise">Fairmont Chateau<br />Lake Louise</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13078014/fairmont-lake-louise.jpg" alt="Fairmont Chateau in Lake Louise" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">The magnificent Fairmont Chateau offers a high class of accommodation with beautiful scenic views of the surrounding mountains and frozen lake, making this hotel a top choice.<br /><br /><strong>30% off - book by 31st August</strong> <br /><br /><em>Not available on bookings between 23rd December - 2nd January and 12th February - 14th February.</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a04e6e8524a4497fb22cc5de99faf4da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a04e6e8524a4497fb22cc5de99faf4da}" title="Fairmont Chateau Lake Louise"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g4">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/d004f6b2777e4359b8b451a792433e6a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d004f6b2777e4359b8b451a792433e6a}" title="Caribou Lodge">Caribou Lodge<br />Banff</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13077378/les-brevieres-exterior-2.jpg" alt="Caribou Lodge in Banff" data-udi="umb://media/e62aeb38256141be8ebad68eeb8da8a9" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Traditional mountain lodge with great facilities and a prime location.<br /><br /><strong>25% off - book by 31st August</strong> <br /><em>Not available on bookings between 23rd December - 2nd January.</em></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><em><strong>100$ Food &amp; Beverage Credit - book by 30th November</strong><br /><span>Stay 8 or more nights in a Superior room and receive $100 CAD F&amp;B credit per stay per room. </span>Not valid stays 23rd December - 2nd January.</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/d004f6b2777e4359b8b451a792433e6a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d004f6b2777e4359b8b451a792433e6a}#0" title="Caribou Lodge" data-anchor="#0 style="><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a><a data-udi="umb://document/bb34d7a4d58648d4ab82b5f388d5ad13" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bb34d7a4d58648d4ab82b5f388d5ad13}" title="Banff Ptarmigan Inn">Ptarmigan Inn<br />Banff</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13077375/du-golf-les-arcs.jpg" alt="Banff Ptarmigan in Banff" data-udi="umb://media/b64a281019ad471f934a2e1832c9c61b" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Centrally located and steps away from downtown Banff.<br /><br /><strong>25% off - book by 31st August</strong> <br /><em>Not available on bookings between 23rd December - 2nd January.</em></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><em><strong>100$ Food &amp; Beverage Credit - book by 30th November</strong><br /><span>Stay 8 or more nights in a Superior room and receive $100 CAD F&amp;B credit per stay per room. </span>Not valid stays 23rd December - 2nd January.<br /></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/bb34d7a4d58648d4ab82b5f388d5ad13" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bb34d7a4d58648d4ab82b5f388d5ad13}" title="Banff Ptarmigan Inn">Find out more &gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a><a data-udi="umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3}" title="Canada">SkiBig3</a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3}" title="Canada">Lift Pass Offer</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13074440/sb3_ssv_danevans_3.jpg" alt="SkiBig3 Lift Pass Offer" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Prebook your SkiBig3 lift pass with us and we'll have it delivered to your hotel for collection when you check-in.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Save up to 20% on pre-booked lift passes - book by 31st August</strong></p>
<p>Your lift pass will give you access to the SkiBig3 area including; Mount Norquay, Lake Louise and the high altitude Sunshine Village. This is some of Canada's best and most varied skiing and boarding.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3}" title="Canada"><strong>Find your holiday &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
